Titolo: NFL GameDay 98

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: NFL GameDay 98 is a video game developed by Sony Interactive Studios America and published by Sony Computer Entertainment for the PlayStation. It was the first football video game to feature 3D polygonal graphics (it took longer for football games to adopt fully polygonal graphics than other genres because their large number of players and requisite fast pace made it difficult to do so at a reasonable frame rate).

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
